<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<!DOCTYPE document
	PUBLIC "-//UJAC.org//Print Document//EN" 
	"http://ujac.sourceforge.net/ujac-print-document.dtd">

<document size="A4" margin-left="70" margin-right="70" margin-top="70" margin-bottom="70">
	
	<font-def name="small" family="Helvetica" size="8" style="normal"/>
	<font-def name="normal" family="Helvetica" size="12" style="normal"/>
	<font-def name="bold" family="Helvetica" size="12" style="bold"/>
	<font-def name="heading" family="Helvetica" size="16" style="bold"/>
	
	<header padding-bottom="50">
		<header-part>
			<table columns="2" widths="60,40" halign="top">
				<cell><image source="logo.jpg" width="300" scale-to-fit="true" /></cell>
				<cell align="right">
					Reykjavíkurmaraþon<br />
					kt. 590493-2369<br />
					Engjavegi 6, 104 Reykjavík<br />
					Sími 535 3700<br />
					<anchor reference="http://www.marathon.is">www.marathon.is</anchor>
				</cell>
			</table>
		</header-part>
    </header>
    
	<paragraph font="heading" spacing-after="18.0">
		Kvittun fyrir skráningu í Reykjavíkurmaraþon Íslandsbanka 18.ágúst 2012.
	</paragraph>

	<table font="normal" padding="0" columns="2" width="100" widths="25,75" halign="center" border-style="none" spacing-after="18.0">
		<cell>Nafn:</cell>
		<cell font="bold">${name}</cell>
		<cell>Kennitala:</cell>
		<cell font="bold">${personalID}</cell>
		<cell>Bolastærð:</cell>
		<cell font="bold">${shirtSize}</cell>
		<cell>Vegalengd:</cell>
		<cell font="bold">${distance}</cell>
		<cell>Verð:</cell>
		<cell font="bold">${price}</cell>
	</table>
	
	<paragraph font="normal" spacing-after="18.0">
		Afhending gagna fer fram í Laugardalshöll föstudaginn 17.ágúst kl.10:00-19:00.
	</paragraph>
	<paragraph font="normal" spacing-after="18.0">
		Vinsamlegast framvísið þessari kvittun þegar gögnin eru sótt til að flýta fyrir afgreiðslu. Vinsamlegast kynnið ykkur nánari upplýsingar um hlaupið á heimasíðunni <anchor reference="http://www.marathon.is/reykjavikurmaraton">www.marathon.is/reykjavikurmaraton</anchor>.
	</paragraph>
	<paragraph font="normal" spacing-after="18.0">
		Þau sem vilja hlaupa til góðs geta safnað áheitum á vefnum <anchor reference="http://www.hlaupastyrkur.is">www.hlaupastyrkur.is</anchor>.
	</paragraph>
	
	<paragraph font="normal" spacing-after="18.0">
		Kveðja,<br />
		Reykjavíkurmaraþon<br />
		<anchor reference="http://www.marathon.is">www.marathon.is</anchor>
	</paragraph>

	<paragraph>
		Kvittun númer: ${id}
	</paragraph>
</document>